>) and YOLO to run inference on video frames. This script assumes you have =
already installed the necessary packages (<code data-wg-notranslate=3D"">op=
encv-python</code> and <code data-wg-notranslate=3D"">ultralytics</code>).<=
/p><div class=3D"admonition example"><p class=3D"admonition-title">Streamin=
g for-loop</p><div class=3D"highlight"><pre id=3D"__code_89"><span></span><=
